  "aboutMe": {
    "content": "Hi baby, my name is Alison, Im 21 years old and I'm so cute and friendly.  I'm venezuelan, and as you can see in my pictures and video (100% real, no fake), I'm a beautiful girl! <br />\nI live in an apartament in Plaza Castilla where you can come and have unforgetable moments! .<br />\nI like doing and recieving massages, they are very relaxing! <br />\nAs I said, Im in Plaza Castilla, but if you don't want to come to my place, I can go to your hotel or apartment, I do outcalls almost anywhere in Madrid. Feel free to text me by WhatsApp or Telegram if you have any questions! See you soon!",
    "original": "Hi baby, my name is Alison, Im 21 years old and I'm so cute and friendly.  I'm venezuelan, and as you can see in my pictures and video (100% real, no fake), I'm a beautiful girl! <br />\nI live in an apartament in Plaza Castilla where you can come and have unforgetable moments! .<br />\nI like doing and recieving massages, they are very relaxing! <br />\nAs I said, Im in Plaza Castilla, but if you don't want to come to my place, I can go to your hotel or apartment, I do outcalls almost anywhere in Madrid. Feel free to text me by WhatsApp or Telegram if you have any questions! See you soon!",
    "original_language": ""
  },
